title: Michel Camilo Masterclass at LCCM
description:
Jazz Pianist Michel Camilo Masterclass visits LCCM to share with students the highlights of his career, artistic development, harmonic and soloing ideas and the progression of jazz and latin music. 

For more information on our piano courses at LCCM, please visit:

http://www.lccm.org.uk/courses/piano-keyboards/
